  <brief_title>Calcium Dobesilate for Chronic Venous Wounds</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind Multicenter Clinical Trial Comparing the Efficacy of Calcium Dobesilate With Placebo in the Treatment of Ulcer Secondaries to Chronic Venous Disease</official_title>
